reviews.review_description:
Still an unfinished demo with a lot to be developed, but I'd be eager to wait and see how this game can be in the future, because I can clearly feel the fun of the game and which parts can be developed to be a lot better.
Suggestions:
1. Add diverse scenarios, such as entering different planets;
2. Add more weapons, such as laser, electric guns, etc;
3. Add double hands control and more props, like powerful machine guns that need to be handled by two hands, or bombs that can be thrown with the other hand which can trigger aoe;
4. The enemies can be more dynamic, instead of staying where they are they might be able to fly around (just like in the game Swarm).
